HEADWORD: Leninism
<hw>Leninism</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>a form of communism based on
the writings of Marx and Lenin; called also
<altname>Marxism-Leninism</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bolshevism, collectivism, Marxism-Leninism, Marxism,
Sovietism, sovietism.</syn>⟦br⟧
